











Knighthead Capital Management












 Knighthead Capital Management, LLC is a New York-based registered investment adviser founded in 2008. The firm focuses on long-short investments and specializes in event driven, distressed credit  and special situation opportunities across a broad array of industries. 
				

Knighthead Capital Management, LLC 
				1140 Avenue of the Americas
				12th Floor
				New York, NY 10036
				Phone: (212) 356-2900
				

Edward P. Massaro
				Chief Operating Officer
				Phone: (212) 356-2905
				Email: emassaro@knighthead.com 









