Company Overview of Knighthead Master Fund, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Knighthead Master Fund, LP is a hedge fund launched and managed by Knighthead Capital Management, LLC. Knighthead Master Fund, LP was formed in 2008, and is domiciled in United States.


1140 Avenue of the Americas12th FloorNew York, NY 10036United States



