Appellee:
V-MX Holdings LLC, BBO Holdings Inc, Vitro Asset Corp, Troper Services Inc, Amsilco Holdings Inc, Vitro Packaging LLC, Vitro Chemical, Fibers and Mining LLC, VVP Auto Glass Inc, Binswanger Glass Company and Crisa Corporation


Appellant:
Knighthead Master Fund LP, Brookville Horizons Fund LP, Davidson Kempner Distressed Opportunities Fund LP and Lord Abbett Bond-Debenture Fund Inc


Case Number:
3:2011cv02603


Filed:
October 3, 2011


Court:
Texas Northern District Court


Office:
Dallas Office


County:
Dallas


Presiding Judge:
Barbara M.G. Lynn


Nature of Suit:
Appeal


Cause of Action:
28:0158


Jury Demanded By:
None



